}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== The pictures in the FCC entry and the AC1300 speed match what EDUP calls the EP-9607S. The [[EDUP EP-9607]] has been available for longer and was advertised as AC1200. FCC entry 2AHRDEP-9607 covers multiple model names which EDUP says are identical: * EP-9607 * EP-9607S * EPLINK-6608 * EPLINK-6608S * EPSKY-3307 * EPSKY-3307S * KW-8019 * KW-8019S
